'''匈牙利希臘禮天主教尼賴吉哈佐教區'''是[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]一個[[東儀天主教|東儀天主教]]教區（[[匈牙利希臘禮天主教會|匈牙利希臘禮]]），屬[[匈牙利希臘禮天主教豪伊杜多羅格總教區|豪伊杜多羅格總教區]]。

教區成立於2015年3月20日升為教區。<ref name="Vatican20150320">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e Nomine, 20.03.2015 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/03/20/0201/00454.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721062936/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/03/20/0201/00454.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2015-03-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>現任教區主教為{{link-en|亞伯爾·索奇卡|Ábel Szocska}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 07.04.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/04/07/180407d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721162405/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/04/07/180407d.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=en |date=2018-04-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

